---
<section class="process">
  <div class="process-wrap">
    <span class="reveal label">How It Works</span>
    <h2 class="reveal">From zero to <span class="serif">live</span> in 2 weeks</h2>
    <div class="process-grid stagger">
      <div class="reveal step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Discovery Call</h3>
        <p>15-minute call to understand your business, goals, and what's not working with your current site. I'll show you what's possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Design & Build</h3>
        <p>I pick the perfect template from my library, customize it to your brand, load your content, and wire up booking/contact forms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Review & Launch</h3>
        <p>You review the site, I make revisions until you're thrilled, then launch it on blazing-fast hosting with SSL and a custom domain.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal step">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <h3>Grow & Optimize</h3>
        <p>Monthly maintenance, Google Business optimization, analytics reporting, and ongoing tweaks to keep you ranking and booking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .process{padding:100px 24px;background:var(--bg-el);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .process-wrap{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
  .process h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:12px 0 48px}
  .process-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px}@media(max-width:900px){.process-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}@media(max-width:500px){.process-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .step{padding:28px 20px}
  .step-num{font-size:48px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:var(--border-lt);margin-bottom:12px}
  .step h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}.step p{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.7}
</style>
